HEADWORD: Digamy
<hw>Dig"a*my</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a second
marriage; <grk>di-</grk> = <grk>di`s-</grk> twice + <?/ marriage. Cf.
<er>Bigamy</er>.]</ety> <def>Act, or state, of being twice married;
deuterogamy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
